1) Unzip horoscope_slots.zip to folder ./horoscope-slots
2) Edit firebase-config.js with your Firebase values
3) Test locally: python3 -m http.server 8000 → http://localhost:8000
4) Create GitHub repo 'horoscope-slots'
5) Upload all files via GitHub web UI (Add file → Upload files)
6) Commit, then Settings → Pages → main branch → Save
7) Open published URL → test signup & spin
8) Record promo.html if you want a video
9) Use PWABuilder to generate Android AAB for Play Store
10) For App Store, use PWABuilder iOS wrapper and Xcode
